criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover/Define — frames the decision problem and objective (value creation at 8.5% WACC);  
Represent — describes the cash‑flow structure and timeline before coding;  
Implement — translates the model into parameterized Python code, custom NPV/IRR, and reports numeric outputs;  
Validate — documents manual checks (sign, terminal tax, discounted cash flow);  
Evolve — runs sensitivity scenarios (20% revenue drop, WACC shifts) and visualizes results;  
Reflect — connects lessons to DRIVER principles and provides executive recommendation.
